   T

   he Division of Atmospheric Sciences supports research to
   add new understanding of the behavior of the earth's atmosphere and its
   interactions with the sun.
   INCLUDING Studies of the physics, chemistry, and dynamics
   of earth's upper and lower atmosphere and its space environment...
